derestimate Trump, and another to not overestimate him. The comments above =
are consolidations of two commonly held views representing the division of =
the nation on Trump. I have written in some books (The Storm Before the Cal=
m) and articles on the forces leading to the intensity of this division, wh=
ich doesn=E2=80=99t fit into the space available here, but from my point of=
 view this divided feeling of the two comments demonstrates the health of o=
ur democracy.&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;<br>
